  reading:{title:"The Lower Moons' Fear",
    en:"After Rui died, Muzan was very angry. He called the remaining Lower Moons to a secret meeting. Kamanue, the Lower Rank Six, was standing in the dark room while the other demons were waiting nervously. Muzan said that the Lower Moons were too weak, and one by one he destroyed them. While Kamanue was trying to explain himself, he was thinking of a way to escape. He told Muzan that he had a plan to grow stronger, but it was too late. Muzan did not listen. The other demons watched in terror as their master showed no mercy. That night taught every demon a hard lesson: in Muzan's world, weakness meant death. Only the Upper Moons, who were far stronger, were allowed to live and serve the demon king.",
    zh:"累死後，無慘大為震怒，召集殘存的下弦之鬼開祕密會議。下弦之陸釜鵺站在黑暗的房間裡，其他鬼則緊張地等待。無慘說下弦太弱，便一個接一個地將他們毀滅。當釜鵺正試圖為自己辯解時，他正想著逃跑的方法。他告訴無慘自己有變強的計畫，但為時已晚，無慘並不理會。其他鬼驚恐地看著主子毫不留情。那一夜給所有鬼上了殘酷的一課：在無慘的世界裡，軟弱就是死亡。只有遠比下弦強大的上弦之鬼才被允許存活、繼續侍奉鬼王。"},
