  reading:{title:"A Promise of Power",
    en:"Mukago was the Lower Rank Four. Like the other Lower Moons, she was terrified when Muzan appeared. \"I can become stronger if you give me more blood,\" she begged. \"I will catch more humans for you, I promise.\" But Muzan only asked a cold question: \"What will you do that the others could not?\" Mukago could not answer. She could feel her own death coming closer. In Muzan's eyes, a demon who could not win was useless. \"You are not going to serve me anymore,\" he said quietly. Far away, Tanjiro was training even harder, because he knew the road ahead would be dangerous. He could already use Water Breathing well, but he was going to learn to fight demons that were much stronger than Rui.",
    zh:"零余子是下弦之肆。和其他下弦一樣，無慘現身時她驚恐萬分。「只要給我更多血，我就能變強，」她哀求。「我會替你抓更多人類，我保證。」但無慘只冷冷地問：「你能做到其他鬼做不到的什麼事？」零余子答不出來，能感到死亡正逼近。在無慘眼中，無法取勝的鬼毫無用處。「你不會再侍奉我了，」他靜靜地說。遠方，炭治郎更加努力訓練，因他知道前路凶險。他已能熟練使用水之呼吸，但他打算學會對付比累強大得多的鬼。"},
